OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA chilly but bright start will
OL,6,Flead to a dry and fine day across the
OL,7,Fregion, with plenty of sunshine. The
OL,8,Fsunshine will turn a little hazy come
OL,9,Fthe afternoon. Feeling warm in the
OL,10,Fsunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA fine evening with some late
OL,13,Fsunshine. Overnight will remain dry
OL,14,Fwith further clear spells. A little
OL,15,Fchilly in the countryside but not as
OL,16,Fcold as recent nights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
