OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FRemaining dry on Wednesday
OL,6,Fwith spells of sunshine, although
OL,7,Fperhaps a little more cloud than
OL,8,Ftoday. Staying warm, especially in the
OL,9,Fsouth of the region.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FCooler and more changeable on
OL,13,FThursday, with spells of rain and
OL,14,Fshowers. Likely to stay unsettled on
OL,15,FFriday and Saturday with further rain
OL,16,Fat times, and temperatures near
OL,17,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
